Contract Labeled
  Teach Label using Self

Record User follows Labeled
  Has Name as String

  Teach Label using Self
    "User {Name of Self}"

Object Counter follows Labeled
  Has Value as Int

  Teach Label using Self
    "Counter {Value of Self}"

Make Ada be New User with Name be "Ada"
Make Count be New Counter with Value be 3

Expect Use Label of Ada is "User Ada"
Expect Use Label of Count is "Counter 3"
